block content
  p 
    | Norska provides the ability to style elements like list items, even if not
    | technically part of a #[code ul]/#[code li], by adding the #[code .bullet] class to them.

  p
   | The default bullet is a circle of the same color as the text, but both the
   | type and color of the bullet can be styled through the #[code .bullet-*]
   | classes. 

  +tailwind_table_header
  each key in data.tailwind.theme('bullet')
    - className = `bullet-${key}`.replace('-default', '')
    +tailwind_table_line(className)
      .w-100p(class=className) Hello World
  -
    examples = [
      ['bullet-tick', 'green'],
      ['bullet-tick', 'bullet-green'],
    ]
  each key in examples
    +tailwind_table_line(key.join('.'))
      .w-100p(class=key) Hello World
